                  <objectDesc>
                     <supportDesc>
                        <support>1 papyrus ; 13.7 x 12.5 cm</support>
                        <condition>
                           <ab type="conservation">Broken off at all sides.</ab>
                        </condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout>
                           <ab type="lines">31 lines</ab>
                           <ab type="recto-verso">Source of description: Recto</ab>
                        </layout>
                     </layoutDesc>
                  </objectDesc>
                  <handDesc>
                     <p>The papyrus is disolved from cartonage and contains the right and left parts respectively of two columns. Upper margin: 2.5 cm.  Intercolumnar area is about 1.5 cm wide. The papyrus is an palimpsest Average height of the letters about 3 mm. The handwriting is careful and elegant without ligatures. Iota adscript is twice included and twice omitted. There is no punctuation or diacritical marks</p>
                  </handDesc>
